  "Description": {
    "English": "Advanced material, processed from regular <span class=\"name name-fuel\">carbon</span> in a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Refiner</span>.<br><br>The increased molecule density offers a substantially improved energy-per-gram ratio.<br><br>Occasionally found in crystalline form. Harvesting large crystals may require a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Advanced Mining Laser</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>将普通<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳</span>加工后的高级材料。<br><br>强化后的分子密度能够极大提升每克能量比例。<br><br>有时呈现晶体形态。可能需要<span class=\"name name-technology\">先进的开采激光</span>来收获大量水晶。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "先進材料，以<span class=\"name name-technology\">精製機</span>加工一般的<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳</span>而成。<br><br>分子濃度上升，大幅提升每單位重量可提供的能量。<br><br>有時呈結晶形態。可能需要<span class=\"name name-technology\">先進採礦雷射</span>才能採集大型結晶。"
  },
